我猜你就隐藏在芸芸众生之中
Guess you're out there, hiding in plain sight.

729
00:38:59,690 --> 00:39:01,790
我一直在找你
I keep looking for you.

730
00:39:01,790 --> 00:39:05,590
而我每次都会陷入糟糕的处境
I keep finding myself in some bad situations.

731
00:39:10,130 --> 00:39:12,880
你也可以随时收手
You could always stop looking for me.

732
00:39:13,870 --> 00:39:15,380
绝不可能
Not an option.

733
00:39:16,070 --> 00:39:17,800
现在又死了两个人
Now I've got two more bodies.

734
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:21,010
我知道人不是你杀的
I don't think you killed those guys.

735
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,730
但我觉得你知道是谁干的
But I think you know who did.

736
00:39:24,640 --> 00:39:26,660
我会处理好
I'll take care of it.

737
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:29,400
一直在玩危险游戏啊
Playing a dangerous game.

738
00:39:29,690 --> 00:39:31,980
我不知道我能不能理解原因
And I'm not sure I understand why.

739
00:39:31,980 --> 00:39:34,180
我有我自己的原因
I've got my reasons.

740
00:39:34,680 --> 00:39:35,580
也许你有
Maybe you do.

741
00:39:36,860 --> 00:39:39,750
但我抓到的每个杀手都以为自己有足够的理由
But every killer I locked up thought they had a good reason.

742
00:39:39,950 --> 00:39:41,230
而他们的结局也是这样
And that is how this ends.

743
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:43,830
我迟早会抓到你
Sooner or later, I'll lock you up.

744
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:46,640
或是在某处发现你的尸体
Or find you bleeding out somewhere.

745
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,760
那就试试看吧
I will take my chances.

746
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:55,010
我能记得的就是这些了
I think I've told you everything that I can remember.

747
00:40:03,330 --> 00:40:04,970
警探  过来这边
Detective, over here.

748
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:08,630
看来他们只拿了这个
Looks like this is all they took.

749
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:17,030
这么说  你放走了那个抢劫犯啊
So you let our bank robber get away.

750
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:20,940
他付出了代价  应该有第二次机会
He paid his dues, deserved a second chance.

751
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:22,140
那这事算完了吗
Then are we done?

752
00:40:22,140 --> 00:40:23,600
还没完
Not quite.

753
00:40:30,210 --> 00:40:32,370
希望这就是你要的东西
I hope that's what you wanted.

754
00:40:42,230 --> 00:40:45,290
那我们来谈谈价钱吧
So we better talk money.

755
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:06,140
看来有人捷足先登了
Someone got here first.

756
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,070
他已经死了
He's dead.

757
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,310
知道是谁干的吗
Any idea who did it?

758
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:14,970
证据盒上的名字是以利亚
The name on the evidence box was Elias.

759
00:41:15,230 --> 00:41:16,720
你有印象吗
That mean anything to you?

760
00:41:16,960 --> 00:41:17,990
没有
No.

761
00:41:19,630 --> 00:41:21,630
我去查查
I'd better look into it.

762
00:42:14,650 --> 00:42:18,520
事实上是  一个人对你来说更容易
The truth is that, it was easier for you to be alone.

763
00:42:20,460 --> 00:42:22,890
这是你在那边学到的东西
That's one of the things you learn over there.

764
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:25,060
到头来  我们都是一个人
In the end, we're all alone.

765
00:42:26,060 --> 00:42:27,800
没有人会来救你
And no one's coming to save you.

766
00:42:29,470 --> 00:42:30,910
祝你和彼得幸福
Be happy with Peter.

767
00:42:31,500 --> 00:42:32,790
你不是真心的
You don't believe that.

768
00:42:33,140 --> 00:42:34,440
不是
Not really.

769
00:42:37,180 --> 00:42:39,250
你想勇敢一次吗
You wanna be brave?

770
00:42:40,150 --> 00:42:41,230
那就冒险一次
Take a risk.

771
00:42:43,250 --> 00:42:44,970
让我等你
Tell me to wait for you and...

772
00:42:47,050 --> 00:42:48,680
只要你说我就答应
Say those words and I will.

773
00:43:00,660 --> 00:43:02,550
这需要极大的勇气吧
It would take real courage, wouldn't it?

774
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:18,390
等我
Wait for me.

775
00:43:20,590 --> 00:43:21,570
求你了
Please.

